                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8923" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1362</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1151 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">套期保值，以期定产：期现结合护航玻璃企业稳健发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hedging to Determine Production: Applying Futures to Promote the Stable Development of Glass Enterprises</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">邓尚昆，朱应可，王炳森，黄诗舒</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">三峡大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆金富源新材料有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化学工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">6 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">玻璃生产企业；期现结合；套期保值</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Glass Manufacturers; Integration of Futures and Spot Markets; Hedge Against Risk</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022年以来，玻璃行业正处于供需矛盾失衡的严峻局面，市场行情的不确定性给玻璃制造企业带来了巨大挑战。一方面，玻璃价格的暴涨带来企业生产的快速扩张；另一方面，玻璃价格的暴跌也导致玻璃库存的增加及亏损的扩大。因此，玻璃制造企业需寻求创新的解决方案来应对市场大幅波动带来的挑战，以确保企业的稳健发展。本案例通过对老张玻璃制造厂在生产运营及价格风险管理方面所面临的困境进行分析，重点介绍玻璃制造企业如何通过有效引入期货工作进行套期保值来规避玻璃行业的市场风险。本案例旨在帮助学员深入了解期货交易、期现结合、套期保值等重要概念及其作用，有助于培养学员熟悉玻璃企业合理运用期货工具的能力，同时对熟悉其他大宗商品相关制造型企业的风险控制具有启发作用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Since 2022, the glass industry is in a severe situation of imbalance between supply and demand, and the uncertainty of market conditions has brought great challenges to glass manufacturing enterprises. On the one hand, the surge in glass prices has led to the rapid expansion of production; on the other hand, the plunge in glass prices has led to the increase in glass inventory and the expansion of losses. Therefore, glass manufacturers need to find innovative solutions to cope with the challenges posed by large market fluctuations in order to ensure the sound development of their businesses. This case analyzes the dilemma faced by Lao Zhang Glass Manufacturing Factory in terms of production operation and price risk management, and focuses on how glass manufacturing enterprises can effectively introduce futures work for hedging to avoid market risks in the glass industry. The case is designed to help participants gain a deeper understanding of the important concepts of futures trading, combining futures with cash and hedging, and their roles, which will help to cultivate the participants&#39; ability to familiarize themselves with the rational use of futures tools in glass enterprises, and at the same time inspire them to familiarize themselves with the risk control of other commodities-related manufacturing enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《风险管理》、《金融市场学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">风险管理；期货交易；套期保值</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
